		Design-a-Weapon catagory 1H Shieldmate

	</td>
	
		<td class="subjectbar" align=right style="padding:0px;padding-right:10px;">












		<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 border=0 id="io_bwarriorbalancem12609_table" 
		
