			<p>
			






<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
Reply <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=warriorbalance&message.id=12609#M12609">1</a> of 1531
</span>

			<br><img src="/i/p.gif" width=1 height=6><br>
			<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
			
					Viewed 2691 times<br>
					
			</span>
			
		</td>
		
		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			In the event SoE does not make changes that reduce the insuperable disadvantages Warriors face when using a shield, the only real alternative is a new weapon type - 1 Handers with ratios simular to Knight weapons and procratemods sufficiently high so that we can continue to hold aggro and not lose 40%+ of our aggro procs when switching from DW to sword and board.<br><br>I thought it would be FUN to see us put together some "fan-designs" much like players of other games produce fan art. Obviously SoE is working feverishly on this problem and doesn't need our input, but it would be fun.<br><br>Endgame 1HS example:<br>Warblade of Rallos Zek<br>90DMG 35DLY 50AC +20 all Stats and Saves, 350HP, 350END WAR LORE MAGIC NO TRADE SHIELDMATE (can not be used with a weapon in the off hand) Effect of Anger IV (increase Hate by 800?) procratemod 90.	
		</td></tr>
		<tr>
		
		<td class="msg_date_cell" valign=bottom nowrap>
		<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
		 <span class=date_text>11-26-2005</span> <span class=time_text>03:06 PM</span>
		</span>
		</td>

		
