Naubi wrote:<BR>Even with the superior 1hs, SKs were KS'd (when it mattered for exp) by their *green* con pet... back in kunark. Perhaps where we are now is considered to be balanced. And remember that the melee revaming went in in middle velious (back when verant were still running the show).<BR><BR>i.e. warriors are forced to choose between at least 2 of their weapon set ups (duel wield for max aggro and max dps, shield for when aggro is established and max defense). Just like knights are forced to choose (remember that, saying it again sorry, our 1h dps is worse than yours even with the better ratio weapons we have).<BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<DIV>Our duel wield is better then your 1h, with the weapon ratio difference. I think BB is suggesting 1hander's that have to be used with a shield, and are made Warrior only. These would be almost as good as doing Duel wield, but still wouldn't be the main aggro set-up. It would however be a good defensive/dps/offensive setup for when we need to change for more defensive, without lossing half of our aggro. It would allow us to get use of a shield, which I hope would go for warrior's of all level's, not just level 70, lol. </FONT></DIV>
<DIV></FONT></DIV>
<DIV>I hope something like this is implemented into the game, and is found on all level's of class progression, from level 1 to level 70.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>The only thing I dissagree with actually, is that it would be Warrior only. I think these weapons should also be usable by Ranger's. It should NEVER be usable by Knight's. It should be consider'd a weapon "below" them if nothing else, even if the ratio and damage is better then there setup.</FONT></DIV><p>Message Edited by JazzyJoyce on <span class=date_text>11-27-2005</span> <span class=time_text>05:57 AM</span>
