<DIV>It's all about getting the perks (the aggro) without giving up the nice mana tap procs or group heal procs.&nbsp; Who cares that they so outclass warriors at the low end now that it's sad, who cares that the gap in initial aggro *without* the EoA belt is completely insurmountable nowdays.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
